Laparoscopy-assisted hepatectomy versus conventional (open) hepatectomy for 
living donors: when you know better, you do better.

Makki K(1), Chorasiya VK, Sood G, Srivastava PK, Dargan P, Vij V.

Author information:
(1)Department of Liver Transplantation, Fortis Hospital, Noida, India.
